Hi,

This app demos how to integrate Facebook and post to your Facebook wall with your own Android app.

Original Source: http://www.integratingstuff.com/2010/10/14/integrating-facebook-into-an-android-application/

I have modified this a bit to make it suit to my needs.
Works well on Motorola Atrix, OS 2.3.4.


Some of the other useful links:

1. http://www.londatiga.net/it/how-to-use-facebook-sdk-to-post-status-from-android/

2. http://ericosgood.com/prog/facebook-android-sdk-tutorial/

3. http://stackoverflow.com/questions/2953146/android-java-post-simple-text-to-facebook-wall

4. http://android10.org/index.php/articleslibraries/290-facebook-integration-in-your-android-application